description: Best practices for integrating Stripe payments
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx}

- Use Stripe's official TypeScript SDK for type-safe integration.
- Implement server-side validation and error handling for payment processes.
- Use Stripe's Webhooks for real-time payment status updates.
- Implement proper error handling and user feedback for payment failures.
- Use Stripe's Elements for secure and customizable payment forms.